  88,17,"afla yanzur alkafirun almkdhdhibwn 'iilaa al'ibl: kayf khuliqat hdha alkhalq alejyb? wa'iilaa alsama' kayf rufieat hdha alrrafe albdye? wa'iilaa aljibal kayf nusbt, fhsl biha althbat llard walastqrar? wa'iilaa al'ard kayf busitt wmuhhidt?"
