  89,5,"'uqsim allah subhanah bwqt alfjr, wallyaly aleashr alawal min dhi alhujat wama shrft bh, wbkl shfe wfrd, wabiallayl 'iidha yasry bzlamh, 'alays fi alaqsam almadhkurat maqnae lidhi eql?"
  89,6,"alm tar -ayha alrswl- kayf faeal rbbuk biqawm ead, qbylt 'irm, dhat alquat walabnyt almrfwet ealaa alaemdt, alati lam yukhlq mithluha fi albilad fi eizam alajsad waquat albas?"
  89,7,"alm tar -ayha alrswl- kayf faeal rbbuk biqawm ead, qbylt 'irm, dhat alquat walabnyt almrfwet ealaa alaemdt, alati lam yukhlq mithluha fi albilad fi eizam alajsad waquat albas?"
  89,8,"alm tar -ayha alrswl- kayf faeal rbbuk biqawm ead, qbylt 'irm, dhat alquat walabnyt almrfwet ealaa alaemdt, alati lam yukhlq mithluha fi albilad fi eizam alajsad waquat albas?"
  89,9,wkyf faeal bthmwd qawm salih aladhin qteu alsakhr balwady watakhadhuu minh bywtana?
  89,10,"wkyf faeal bfrewn malik \"msr\", sahib aljunud aldhyn thbbatu mulkh, wqwwu lah amrh?"
  89,11,"hwla' aladhin astbddu, wazalamuu fi bilad allh, fa'aktharuu fiha bizulmihim alfsad, fasaba ealayhim rbbuk eadhabana shdyda. 'inn rabak -ayha alrswl- labialmirsad liman yesyh, ymhlh qalilana thuma yakhudhh akhdh eaziz mqtdr"
