  89,17,"lys al'amr kama yazunu hdha al'insan, bal al'ikram btaet allh, wal'ihant bmesyth, wa'antum laa tukrimun alytym, wala thsnwn meamlth, wala yahuthth baedukum bedana ealaa 'iiteam almskyn, watakulun huquq alakharin fi almirath 'aklana shdydana, watuhibuwn almal hbana mfrtana"
