  89,24,"yqwl: ya laytani qddamt fi aldunya min al'aemal ma ynfeny lihayati fi alakhrt"
  89,25,"ffy dhlk alyawm aleasib la yastatie ahd wala yuqadar 'ana yuedhdhib mithl taedhib allah min esah, wala yastatie 'ahad 'an ywthiq mithl wthaq allh, wala yablugh ahd mblghh fi dhlk"
