  89,27,"ya 'ayatuha alnafs almutmayinat 'iilaa dhikr allah wal'iiman bh, wabima aeddah min alnaeim llmwmnyn, arjiei 'iilaa rabik radiatan b'ikram allah lk, wallah subhanah qad radi enk, fadkhuli fi eidad eibad allah alsalhyn, wadkhuli maeahum jnty"
